quran[19{c,v,t}:
15,52,"jab woh aeye uss ke haan aur kaha"" salam ho tum par,"" to uss ne kaha"" hamein tum se dar lagta hai """
15,53,"onhon ne jawab diya"" daro nahi, hum tumhe aik barray syane larke ki basharat dete hain """
15,54,"ibrahim ne kaha"" kya tum iss burhapay mein mujhe aulaad ki basharat dete ho? zara socho to sahi ke yeh kaisi basharat tum mujhe day rahay ho? """
15,55,"onhon ne jawab diya"" hum tumhe brhq basharat day rahay hain, tum mayoos nah ho """
15,56,"ibrahim ne kaha"" apne rab ki rehmat se mayoos to gumraah log hi howa karte hain """
15,57,"phir ibrahim ne poocha"" ae faristganeEllahi, woh muhim kya hai jis par aap hazraat tashreef laaye hain? """
15,58,"woh bolay,"" hum aik mujrim qoum ki taraf beje gay hain"
15,59,"sirf loot ke ghar walay mustasna hain, un sab ko hum bacha len ge"
15,60,"siwaye uss ki biwi ke jis ke liye ( Allah farmata hai ke ) hum ne muqaddar kar diya hai ke woh peechay reh jaane walon mein shaamil rahay gi """
15,61,phir jab yeh fristadayloot ke haan puhanche
15,62,"to uss ne kaha"" aap log ajnabi maloom hotay hain """
15,63,"onhon ne jawab diya"" nahi, balkay hum wohi cheez le kar aeye hain jis ke anay mein yeh log shak kar rahay thay"
15,64,hum tum se sach kehte hain ke hum haq ke sath tumahray paas aeye hain
15,65,"lehaza ab tum kuch raat rahay apne ghar walon ko le kar nikal jao aur khud un ke peechay peechay chalo tum mein se koi palat kar nah dekhe bas seedhay chalay jao jidhar jaane ka tumhe hukum diya ja raha hai """
15,66,aur ussay hum ne apna yeh faisla pouncha diya ke subah hotay hotay inn logon ki jarr kaat di jaye gi
15,67,itnay mein shehar ke log khusi ke maaray be taab ho kar loot ke ghar charh aeye
15,68,"loot ne kaha"" bhayio, yeh mere mehman hain, meri fazihat nah karo"
15,69,"Allah se daro, mujhe ruswa nah karo """
15,70,"woh bolay"" kya hum baarha tumhe mana nahi kar chuke hain ke duniya bhar ke thekay daar nah bano? """
